{"word":"H4725 - מָקֹום - mâqôwm - maw-kome' - Country","slug":"H4725","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָקֹום</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mâqôwm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-kome'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Country"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E7;&#x05DE;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05E7;&#x05D5;&#x05DE;&#x05D4;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05E7;&#x05DD;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05E7;&#x05D5;&#x05DD; - ma&#x0302;qo&#x0302;m  ma&#x0302;qo&#x0302;m  m<sup>e</sup>qo&#x0302;ma&#x0302;h  m<sup>e</sup>qo&#x0302;ma&#x0302;h</b> - <i>(1,2) maw-kome', (3,4) mek-o-mah'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6965\">H6965</a>; properly a <i>standing</i>, that is, a <i>spot</i>; but used widely of a <i>locality</i> (generally or specifically); also (figuratively) of a <i>condition</i> (of body or mind): - country, X home, X open, place, room, space, X whither [-soever]."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3351\">H3351</a>, <a href=\"#/H3356\">H3356</a>, <a href=\"#/H3359\">H3359</a>, <a href=\"#/H3360\">H3360</a>, <a href=\"#/H3361\">H3361</a>, <a href=\"#/H6965\">H6965</a>, <a href=\"#/H6967\">H6967</a>, <a href=\"#/H6968\">H6968</a>, <a href=\"#/H6970\">H6970</a>, <a href=\"#/H6971\">H6971</a>, <a href=\"#/H7009\">H7009</a>, <a href=\"#/H7012\">H7012</a>, <a href=\"#/H7054\">H7054</a>, <a href=\"#/H7056\">H7056</a>, <a href=\"#/H8617\">H8617</a>, <a href=\"#/H8618\">H8618</a>"}]}